 <name>tokenizers</name>
 <channel>pecl.php.net</channel>
 <summary>Fast BPE tokenizer extension (cl100k_base, p50k, r50k, o200k)</summary>
 <description>
  A PHP extension providing a fast Byte-Pair Encoding (BPE) tokenizer
  compatible with OpenAI encodings (cl100k_base, p50k_base, r50k_base,
  o200k_base). The core merge loop is implemented in C for performance
  and uses O(n log n) heap-based merging. Vocabulary files are
  downloaded and checksum-verified on first use via a bundled PHP shim;
  they are never redistributed with the package.
 </description>
